PN,30701
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778652345
OL,3,CSome of UK's most popular sandwiches
OL,4,Ccontain 'alarmingly high' levels of
OL,5,Csalt
OL,7,FSome of the UK's most popular shop-
OL,8,Fbought sandwiches contain "alarmingly
OL,9,Fhigh" levels of salt, with one
OL,10,Fcontaining more than almost five
OL,11,FMcDonald's cheeseburgers, according to
OL,12,Fa study.
OL,14,FAction on Salt & Sugar analysed 546
OL,15,Fsandwiches, wraps, rolls and baguettes
OL,16,Fsold in supermarkets and high street
OL,17,Fchains to find that one in 10 exceed
OL,18,Fthe salt and calorie health targets.
OL,26,@pD@[OUqD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778652345
OL,3,CSome of UK's most popular sandwiches
OL,4,Ccontain 'alarmingly high' levels of
OL,5,Csalt
OL,7,FAlmost half (44%) would carry a red or
OL,8,F"high" salt warning on their front-of-
OL,9,Fpack labelling, while 32 deliver half
OL,10,For more of an adult's maximum daily
OL,11,Flimit in a single serving, it found.
OL,13,FAction on Salt & Sugar said the
OL,14,Ffindings laid bare the scale of hidden
OL,15,Fsalt in everyday lunch choices and
OL,16,Fexposed the "failure" of the
OL,17,FGovernment's voluntary approach to
OL,18,Fimproving the nutritional quality of
OL,19,Ffood.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@FO]xD@MOUxD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778652345
OL,3,CSome of UK's most popular sandwiches
OL,4,Ccontain 'alarmingly high' levels of
OL,5,Csalt
OL,7,FThe charity named the Smoked Chicken
OL,8,FCaesar Club sold by upmarket cafe
OL,9,Fchain Gail's as the "worst offender",
OL,10,Ffinding that it contained a
OL,11,F"staggering" 6.88g of salt, equivalent
OL,12,Fto nearly 10 rashers of bacon or five
OL,13,FMcDonald's cheeseburgers.
OL,15,FAdults should consume no more than 6g
OL,16,Fof salt a day ` or around one level
OL,17,Fteaspoon ` according to UK health
OL,18,Fguidelines.
OL,26,@qD@UOUqD@dO]sD@AOUsD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778652345
OL,3,CSome of UK's most popular sandwiches
OL,4,Ccontain 'alarmingly high' levels of
OL,5,Csalt
OL,7,FFurthermore, the sandwich also
OL,8,Fcontains 1,067 calories and 90% of an
OL,9,Fadult's maximum daily saturated fat
OL,10,Flimit, while providing only 20% of an
OL,11,Fadult's recommended fibre intake, the
OL,12,Fstudy found.
OL,14,FHowever, the wider picture was equally
OL,15,Fpoor, with researchers finding that a
OL,16,Fthird of sandwiches surveyed would
OL,17,Freceive a red warning on front-of-pack
OL,18,Flabelling for saturated fat, and more
OL,19,Fthan one in seven high in fat,
OL,20,Fsaturated fat and salt simultaneously.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778652345
OL,3,CSome of UK's most popular sandwiches
OL,4,Ccontain 'alarmingly high' levels of
OL,5,Csalt
OL,7,FAlmost all the sandwiches surveyed
OL,8,F(97%) failed to provide even a third
OL,9,Fof the daily recommended fibre intake.
OL,11,FA quarter of the sandwiches (25%) are
OL,12,Fclassified as "less healthy" under the
OL,13,Fcurrent 2004/5 Nutrient Profiling
OL,14,FModel, limiting how and where they can
OL,15,Fbe promoted to shoppers.
OL,17,FThe research found that sandwiches
OL,18,Fbought out-of-home (OOH) were
OL,19,Fgenerally saltier than those sold in
OL,20,Fsupermarkets.
OL,26,@tD@OOUtD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778652345
OL,3,CSome of UK's most popular sandwiches
OL,4,Ccontain 'alarmingly high' levels of
OL,5,Csalt
OL,7,FAmong the poorest performers with
OL,8,Fnaturally salty or heavily processed
OL,9,Fingredients were Gail's Smoked Salmon
OL,10,FBagel with Schmear and Pickled Pink
OL,11,FOnions containing 4.2g of salt, and
OL,12,FPaul's Rosette Cheese Salami Gherkin,
OL,13,Fcontaining 4.19g of salt, the study
OL,14,Ffound.
OL,16,FThis was followed by Pret A Manger's
OL,17,FHam & Greve Baguette with 3.85g per
OL,18,Fserving.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778652345
OL,3,CSome of UK's most popular sandwiches
OL,4,Ccontain 'alarmingly high' levels of
OL,5,Csalt
OL,7,FThe study found that other products
OL,8,Fparticularly high in salt included
OL,9,FTesco's Fully Loaded Hot Honey
OL,10,FHalloumi, Falafel and Pickled Slaw at
OL,11,F3.78g, Tootoomoo's Sriracha Pork Sando
OL,12,Fat 3.67g and Sainsbury's Kitchen Deli
OL,13,FPastrami, Cheddar Cheese & Gherkin
OL,14,FMustard Mayo at 3.67g ` all containing
OL,15,Fmore salt than 12 standard bags of
OL,16,Fready salted crisps.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778652345
OL,3,CSome of UK's most popular sandwiches
OL,4,Ccontain 'alarmingly high' levels of
OL,5,Csalt
OL,7,FHowever, Action on Salt & Sugar found
OL,8,Fwide differences in the salt content
OL,9,Fof similar sandwiches and fillings,
OL,10,Fsuch as Pret A Manger's Chicken Salad
OL,11,FSandwich containing 2.22g of salt, and
OL,12,FGreggs' Roast Chicken Salad Sandwich
OL,13,Fcontaining half as much again with
OL,14,F1.1g of salt.
OL,16,FSimilarly, an M&S All Day Breakfast
OL,17,FSandwich contained 2.65g of salt,
OL,18,Fcompared with 1.54g in Sainsbury's All
OL,19,FDay Breakfast Sandwich.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778652345
OL,3,CSome of UK's most popular sandwiches
OL,4,Ccontain 'alarmingly high' levels of
OL,5,Csalt
OL,7,FAction on Salt & Sugar said several
OL,8,Flower-salt products showed that
OL,9,Freformulation was "both possible and
OL,10,Fpractical", including Subway's Veggie
OL,11,FDelite Sub with just 0.60g of salt,
OL,12,FPret A Manger's Avo, Olive & Toms Half
OL,13,FBaguette at 0.82g, Caffe Nero's
OL,14,FChicken, Tomato & Basil Hot Wrap at
OL,15,F1.08g, and Greggs' Tuna Mayonnaise &
OL,16,FCucumber Sandwich at 1.1g per serving.
OL,26,@qD@SOUrD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
